{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be sleek and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Artist Portfolio</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #0d47a1; /* Primary brand blue */\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #0d47a1 3px solid;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        #hero {\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/0d47a1/ffffff?text=Artist+Artwork') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            min-height: 400px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #about, #portfolio, #contact {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #about h2, #portfolio h2, #contact h2 {\n            color: #0d47a1;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        .gallery-item {\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            padding: 15px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .gallery-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .gallery-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px; /* Fixed height for consistency */\n            object-fit: cover; /* Ensures image covers the area without distortion */\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .gallery-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: #0d47a1;\n        }\n        .gallery-item p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        form {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            display: inline-block;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        input[type=\"text\"], input[type=\"email\"], textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n        }\n        button {\n            background-color: #0d47a1;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 12px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        button:hover {\n            background-color: #1565c0;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #0d47a1;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>[Artist Name]</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Transforming Visions into Reality</h2>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About the Artist</h2>\n            <p>\n                [Artist Name] is a contemporary artist known for their evocative use of color and texture.\n                With a passion for exploring themes of nature and human emotion, their work invites viewers\n                into a world of vibrant imagination. Based in [City/Region], [Artist Name] has been\n                showcasing their art in galleries and private collections for over a decade.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"portfolio\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Portfolio</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/0d47a1/ffffff?text=Artwork+1\" alt=\"Artwork 1\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 1</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork, its medium, and inspiration.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/1565c0/ffffff?text=Artwork+2\" alt=\"Artwork 2\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 2</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork, its medium, and inspiration.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/1976d2/ffffff?text=Artwork+3\" alt=\"Artwork 3\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 3</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork, its medium, and inspiration.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/2196f3/ffffff?text=Artwork+4\" alt=\"Artwork 4\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 4</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork, its medium, and inspiration.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/42a5f5/ffffff?text=Artwork+5\" alt=\"Artwork 5\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 5</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork, its medium, and inspiration.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"gallery-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/64b5f6/ffffff?text=Artwork+6\" alt=\"Artwork 6\">\n                    <h3>Title of Artwork 6</h3>\n                    <p>A brief description of the artwork, its medium, and inspiration.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <p>Interested in a commission or have a question about my work?</p>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 [Artist Name]. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}